{"word":"Grace, Divine","slug":"grace,-divine","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Grace, Divine</b> - <b>(1) Of God</b><p/>Freely Given<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=11'>Psa 84:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=23'>Act 11:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=43'>Act 13:43</a><p/>Empowers men for service<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=3&verse=10'>1Co 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=10'>1Co 15:10</a><p/>Enables men to lead the Simple Life<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Co 1:12</a><p/>May be rendered ineffectual<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=6&verse=1'>2Co 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=21'>Gal 2:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=3&verse=7'>Eph 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=9'>Heb 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=4&verse=6'>Jas 4:6</a><p/>Not given for selfish use<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=10'>1Pe 4:10</a><p/>Promised to the humble<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=5'>1Pe 5:5</a><p/><b>(2) Of Christ</b><p/><b>Exhibited in Childhood</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=40'>Luk 2:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=17'>Joh 1:17</a><p/><b>Manifested in Self-Sacrifice</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=9'>2Co 8:9</a><p/><b>Sufficient for All Human Needs</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=9'>2Co 12:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=4&verse=7'>Eph 4:7</a><p/><b>Bestowed upon Sinful Men</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=12'>1Ti 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=13'>1Ti 1:13</a><p/><b>The Source of Power</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=2&verse=1'>2Ti 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=22&verse=21'>Rev 22:21</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Spiritual Love LOVE<p/><b>(3) Salvation by</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=11'>Act 15:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=24'>Rom 3:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=5&verse=15'>Rom 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=11&verse=6'>Rom 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=2&verse=5'>Eph 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=11'>Tit 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=3&verse=7'>Tit 3:7</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Good Works, WORK AND WORKERS, RELIGIOUS<p/>Justification (1), JUSTIFICATION<p/>Faith (3), FAITH<p/><b>(4) Riches of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=4'>Rom 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=23'>Rom 9:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=1&verse=7'>Eph 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=2&verse=7'>Eph 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=4&verse=19'>Phi 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=14'>1Ti 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=3&verse=6'>Tit 3:6</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Spiritual Riches, RICHES<p/> RICHES<p/><b>(5) Bestows Unmerited Favours</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=5'>Deu 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=16'>Ro